{"id":1243,"category_slug":"toeic","category_name":"TOEIC Listening","position":204,"title":"Conversation 104","subtitle":"New Policy on Parties","level":"B2","parts":12,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/toeic/conversation-104.1243/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-104-2023-10-03-11-36-38/0-conversation-104.mp3","transcript":"Did you get the memo on the new policy on company parties?\nI can't believe it!\nYeah, Sarah told me about it.\nIt is terrible.\nTen dollars per head for our parties?\nThey are really going to go downhill.\nI know!\nManagement said that we didn't perform to their satisfaction this year,\nso they didn't have the extra money to spend, which is ridiculous\nbecause we only have two parties per year.\nI agree. And they think that this is going to motivate us?\nI am ready to look for a new job.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T21:01:24","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Did you get the memo on the new policy on company parties?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-104-2023-10-03-11-36-38/1.mp3","time_start":0.0,"time_end":3.31},{"position":2,"content":"I can't believe it!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-104-2023-10-03-11-36-38/2.mp3","time_start":3.31,"time_end":4.75},{"position":3,"content":"Yeah, Sarah told me about it.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-104-2023-10-03-11-36-38/3.mp3","time_start":4.75,"time_end":7.28},{"position":4,"content":"It is terrible.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-104-2023-10-03-11-36-38/4.mp3","time_start":7.28,"time_end":8.64},{"position":5,"content":"Ten dollars per head for our parties?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-104-2023-10-03-11-36-38/5.mp3","time_start":8.64,"time_end":11.04},{"position":6,"content":"They are really going to go downhill.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-104-2023-10-03-11-36-38/6.mp3","time_start":11.04,"time_end":13.27},{"position":7,"content":"I know!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-104-2023-10-03-11-36-38/7.mp3","time_start":13.27,"time_end":14.22},{"position":8,"content":"Management said that we didn't perform to their satisfaction this year,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-104-2023-10-03-11-36-38/8-2024-09-20-20-52-53.mp3","time_start":14.22,"time_end":18.47},{"position":9,"content":"so they didn't have the extra money to spend, which is ridiculous","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-104-2023-10-03-11-36-38/9.mp3","time_start":18.47,"time_end":21.69},{"position":10,"content":"because we only have two parties per year.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-104-2023-10-03-11-36-38/10.mp3","time_start":21.69,"time_end":24.16},{"position":11,"content":"I agree. And they think that this is going to motivate us?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-104-2023-10-03-11-36-38/11.mp3","time_start":24.16,"time_end":27.5},{"position":12,"content":"I am ready to look for a new job.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-104-2023-10-03-11-36-38/12.mp3","time_start":27.5,"time_end":29.71}]}